I'm officially out of the court.

05:10.113 --> 05:13.225
I always pegged you
as a in-it-for-life kind of guy.

05:13.249 --> 05:14.949
Well it wasn't my choice.

05:16.219 --> 05:17.896
What, did they slap
a medal on you

05:17.920 --> 05:19.965
and decide you're a better
showpiece than a soldier?

05:19.989 --> 05:21.233
Oh, fuck the medals.

05:21.257 --> 05:22.901
It don't bring back the guys
we lost

05:22.925 --> 05:24.659
no matter how much
you polish them.

05:26.162 --> 05:27.662
I had enough.

05:29.265 --> 05:30.665
It was time.

05:32.402 --> 05:36.315
Well... I guess Viv is happy
you guys are gonna get to spend

05:36.339 --> 05:37.905
some quality time together.

05:38.141 --> 05:39.206
Oorah!

05:39.909 --> 05:41.075
[BARTENDER] On the house.

05:41.344 --> 05:42.287
Why?

05:42.311 --> 05:45.046
I can't have you buy drinks
after all you did over there.

05:45.848 --> 05:47.081
After all I did?

05:47.750 --> 05:48.927
I was just doing my job

05:48.951 --> 05:50.751
just like you should be
doing yours, here.

05:50.920 --> 05:53.721
Hey, relax man. I'm just trying
to show a little respect.

05:54.023 --> 05:56.323
Show some respect
and take the money.

05:58.995 --> 06:00.094
You got it.

06:04.167 --> 06:05.800
I'm sick of that man.

06:06.302 --> 06:08.469
What, free drinks?
I'll take them all day long.

06:09.739 --> 06:12.807
False appreciation,
hiding behind the flag...

06:14.043 --> 06:15.076
It's bullshit.

06:16.946 --> 06:18.079
I just...

06:19.415 --> 06:21.816
