to some normalcy.

06:22.819 --> 06:24.118
I just wanna get...

06:25.054 --> 06:26.454
back to my life.

06:27.957 --> 06:29.857
How is Viv handling all of this?

06:33.830 --> 06:35.262
It's an adjustment.

06:37.767 --> 06:40.234
