to business?

06:43.239 --> 06:44.732
What do you mean?

06:44.756 --> 06:46.316
You know,
working on a little mini Coop?

06:47.076 --> 06:50.344
It's none of your goddamn
business, but yes. Yeah.

06:50.847 --> 06:51.912
A lot?

06:52.315 --> 06:54.059
- Yeah. A lot. A lot.
- [CHUCKLES]

06:54.083 --> 06:57.229
<i>[VIVIAN] Police said at the
early hours of March 22nd,</i>

06:57.253 --> 06:59.732
<i>two owners were found dead
here this morning.</i>

06:59.756 --> 07:01.400
[MAN] That chick
needs to show me her tits.

