07:06.461 --> 07:08.742
[JOHN] Don't even pay attention
to 'em, Coop. C'mon. Coop.

07:08.831 --> 07:10.965
[FRIEND] She needs to do
a report on my balls.

07:16.305 --> 07:17.349
Hey, guys.

07:17.373 --> 07:19.218
I'm a pretty nice dude
which is why

07:19.242 --> 07:21.909
I'm gonna give you a chance
to take back what you just said.

07:22.245 --> 07:24.256
What the fuck is he...
What are you talking about?

07:24.280 --> 07:25.758
