your words

07:25.782 --> 07:27.181
or you can eat this bar.

07:27.917 --> 07:28.961
That's my wife.

07:28.985 --> 07:32.097
Oh, that can't be your wife
anymore man,

07:32.121 --> 07:33.698
that Jack's girl.

07:33.722 --> 07:35.442
Maybe if she's with this guy
I got a chance.

07:36.292 --> 07:37.324
[BOTTLE BREAKS]

07:39.929 --> 07:40.873
[GRUNTS]

07:40.897 --> 07:41.962
C'mon, Coop.

07:43.166 --> 07:45.377
I don't give a shit
if you are a war hero,

07:45.401 --> 07:47.146
