07:47.170 --> 07:49.870
Just go. Get out of here.
Come on.

08:16.465 --> 08:18.432
Guess those medals
are worth something.

08:19.335 --> 08:21.302
They're gonna look
the other way this time.

08:22.939 --> 08:24.483
Last thing they want to do
is answer questions

08:24.507 --> 08:26.552
about a decorated marine
being arrested

08:26.576 --> 08:28.175
for defending his wife's honor.

08:32.248 --> 08:34.458
