09:02.478 --> 09:04.945
Why don't you
and Vivian join me?

09:05.915 --> 09:08.060
To the Virgin Islands?

09:08.084 --> 09:10.629
Yeah, why not? I mean,
a couple days on the open water,

09:10.653 --> 09:12.464
