09:12.488 --> 09:15.267
No, no, no, no, no, no, no, no.

09:15.291 --> 09:19.438
Big guy, I mean...
Yes, Viv loves the water.

09:19.462 --> 09:20.973
Yeah, she does, yeah!

09:20.997 --> 09:24.109
And then you'll be a hero,
to her for once.

09:24.133 --> 09:27.012
I mean if it's God and country
all the time,

09:27.036 --> 09:29.904
it's no good
unless your wife is satisfied.

09:30.573 --> 09:32.006
I'll think about it.

09:32.275 --> 09:33.585
Fuck thinking about it.

09:33.609 --> 09:35.520
Pack your bags,
come down there,

09:35.544 --> 09:37.411
we'll have a great time,
I promise you.

09:37.980 --> 09:39.513
I will think about it.

09:40.616 --> 09:42.049
I'm going to call Viv.

09:43.252 --> 09:44.429
Go ahead, she's at work.

09:44.453 --> 09:46.031
She's not going to pick up
anyways.

09:46.055 --> 09:48.455
- I'll call her after work.
- Let's go, I'm... I'm tired.

10:02.338 --> 10:03.504
[WATER GUSHING]

10:10.079 --> 10:11.211
[VIVIAN] I'm home.

10:12.381 --> 10:13.647
[COOPER] Hey, I'm in here!

10:31.500 --> 10:32.678
You hungry?

10:32.702 --> 10:33.968
Yeah.

10:35.171 --> 10:36.303
Yeah, I am.

10:44.580 --> 10:45.657
Hey.

10:45.681 --> 10:47.942
Look.

10:47.966 --> 10:50.250
- [COOPER] What's that?
- [CHUCKLES]

10:51.320 --> 10:53.247
So handsome.

10:53.271 --> 10:55.200
[COOPER] Oh, thank you.
Did you put him up to this?

10:55.224 --> 10:56.290
Of course.

11:01.530 --> 11:02.596
What happened?

11:04.400 --> 11:05.532
I'm fine.

11:05.701 --> 11:06.701
Coop?

11:08.170 --> 11:10.604
It's a long story. I'm sorry.

11:14.443 --> 11:17.144
Well we have chicken,

11:17.480 --> 11:20.180
stuff for spaghetti, or...

11:22.518 --> 11:24.685
- pistachio ice cream.
- Give me that.

11:26.555 --> 11:29.023
- I won't spoil my dinner.
- [CHUCKLES]

11:34.063 --> 11:35.396
So John called.

11:36.565 --> 11:37.631
Yeah?

11:38.034 --> 11:40.034
He told me about the offer
he made.

11:42.371 --> 11:44.016
- What offer?
- Come on.

11:44.040 --> 11:47.341
He told me about the boat
and going down to the island.

11:48.110 --> 11:51.089
I think it's a good idea.
I think we could use a break.

11:51.113 --> 11:53.514
