12:17.473 --> 12:19.718
You don't take your meds,
you won't go to the VA,

12:19.742 --> 12:21.787
I so much as mention you
seeing a psychiatrist

12:21.811 --> 12:23.243
and you say no.

12:24.280 --> 12:26.180
How am I supposed to fix this?

12:27.116 --> 12:28.148
Huh?

12:32.755 --> 12:33.765
I'm sorry.

12:33.789 --> 12:36.090
No, stop.

12:37.093 --> 12:39.093
I just want my husband back.

14:04.213 --> 14:05.445
Are you awake?

14:10.386 --> 14:11.730
Okay, we can go.

14:11.754 --> 14:14.221
Huh? Go?

14:14.890 --> 14:17.391
Yeah, on the boat
with John, we can go.

14:17.927 --> 14:20.527
[VIVIAN] Mmm. Good.

14:28.637 --> 14:30.682
- [VIVIAN] Do you see it?
- What

14:30.706 --> 14:32.206
I don't see it.

14:33.943 --> 14:35.409
[SIGHS]

14:35.811 --> 14:38.278
[TUTS] Is this how
you're going to be?

14:40.482 --> 14:42.627
Look, if you're just doing this
to keep me quiet

14:42.651 --> 14:44.462
and you're going to be miserable
the entire trip

14:44.486 --> 14:45.830
- then let's just go home.
- I'll be fine.

14:45.854 --> 14:47.399
It's just if he asks me
about the war,

14:47.423 --> 14:49.367
- I'm going to jump overboard.
- He won't.

14:49.391 --> 14:50.602
I told him it was off limits.

14:50.626 --> 14:52.270
Are you sure?
It's like he's obsessed

14:52.294 --> 14:54.238
with death and destruction.

14:54.262 --> 14:56.208
He's an orthopedic surgeon
who has a trust fund

14:56.232 --> 14:57.442
and drives a hybrid.

14:57.466 --> 15:00.000
It's... he just needs
a little adventure.

15:00.336 --> 15:02.617
