15:06.275 --> 15:08.575
John Livingstone, super soldier.

15:11.380 --> 15:12.556
[MIMICS GUNFIRE]

15:12.580 --> 15:13.959
C'mon, he's your brother's
best friend.

15:13.983 --> 15:15.616
