15:16.885 --> 15:18.919
He probably needs this
as much as we do.

15:21.790 --> 15:22.990
Come on.

15:26.428 --> 15:27.494
Come on.

15:37.339 --> 15:38.350
There he is.

15:38.374 --> 15:40.774
[VIVIAN] It's a little early
for that, isn't it?

15:42.578 --> 15:45.023
Who gives a shit,
we are on vacation.

15:45.047 --> 15:46.313
[VIVIAN] Yeah.

15:46.849 --> 15:47.959
