it was going to be.

15:50.486 --> 15:51.529
[CHUCKLES]

15:51.553 --> 15:54.332
- It's a 75-foot Lazara.
- Ah,

15:54.356 --> 15:56.601
- permission to come aboard?
- Oh, how could I refuse,

15:56.625 --> 15:58.625
- look, give that to him.
- Here, I'll take that.

15:58.794 --> 16:00.939
- Let me help you. I got ya.
- Okay. Okay.

16:00.963 --> 16:02.440
- I got ya. [GRUNTS]
- [YELPS]

16:02.464 --> 16:04.498
- It's so good to see you.
- You too, thanks, John.

16:05.601 --> 16:07.934
Make yourself at home,
we got beers up there.

16:10.539 --> 16:11.705
- Hey, man.
- Hey.

16:12.741 --> 16:13.718
[SIGHS]

16:13.742 --> 16:16.637
