than a doctor, so.

16:25.788 --> 16:27.988
You ready for a weekend
that's gonna change your life?

16:28.657 --> 16:30.769
No kumbaya shit
and yeah, I'll be ready.

16:30.793 --> 16:32.659
Well there goes tonight's
entertainment.

16:34.463 --> 16:35.896
So, you know how to run
this thing?

16:36.398 --> 16:38.076
It's not going to be
a 3-hour tour is it?

16:38.100 --> 16:41.780
No, no, no. This baby's
got four 435 horsepower

16:41.804 --> 16:43.648
Volvo diesel inboards.

16:43.672 --> 16:46.640
Get this on the open water
and this baby is going to purr.

16:47.710 --> 16:48.809
<i>Bella Wood?</i>

16:49.778 --> 16:51.456
There's got to be a story there,
huh?

16:51.480 --> 16:53.057
Oh, there is.

16:53.081 --> 16:54.659
