to spill your beer.

17:17.506 --> 17:18.839
This is awesome.

17:20.709 --> 17:22.108
[BEER BOTTLES CLINKING]

17:25.614 --> 17:27.759
Well I guess I should
give you guys the dime tour.

17:27.782 --> 17:29.461
Yeah, let's do it.

17:29.485 --> 17:32.519
All right, we are in the stern
right now.

