of the boat,

17:53.409 --> 17:54.708
anchor's over there,

17:54.910 --> 17:57.544
plenty of room to lay out
and work on your tan.

17:59.515 --> 18:00.580
Hop up.

18:01.617 --> 18:02.660
Thank you.

18:02.684 --> 18:03.750
Come over here.

18:04.887 --> 18:06.731
This is the portside of the boat

18:06.755 --> 18:09.734
and that's the starboard.
Port is the left.

18:09.758 --> 18:10.802
Okay.

18:10.826 --> 18:12.659
Starboard is right obviously.

18:14.062 --> 18:15.128
[CLEARS THROAT]

18:15.898 --> 18:17.442
In here is our salon.

18:17.466 --> 18:19.177
Basically it's your living room.

18:19.201 --> 18:21.546
That the helm station,
nice views, huh?

18:21.570 --> 18:23.014
Yeah, it's beautiful.

18:23.038 --> 18:24.749
Yeah, yeah, close that door,

18:24.773 --> 18:26.584
you sure you don't need help
with the bag?

18:26.608 --> 18:27.719
No, I got the bag.

18:27.743 --> 18:29.703
Follow me. Come down here
and let me help you Viv.

18:29.727 --> 18:31.710
- Thank you.
- Watch your step.

18:34.750 --> 18:38.196
Here we have the galley,
that's the pantry.

18:38.220 --> 18:40.854
It's stocked with beans, rice,
et cetera. Booze.

18:41.089 --> 18:43.701
Oh, yeah. In there,
we've got proteins, meats,

18:43.725 --> 18:45.069
but we'll probably
fish for dinner.

18:45.093 --> 18:46.805
- You guys like seafood, right?
- Yeah, I love it.

18:46.829 --> 18:48.706
All right. And if you
will follow me down here,

18:48.730 --> 18:49.896
this is the cabin.

18:56.472 --> 18:58.917
All right. Now, normally
this is the captain's quarters,

18:58.941 --> 19:00.852
but this weekend it's yours.

19:00.876 --> 19:02.020
No, you don't have to do that.

19:02.044 --> 19:03.655
