21:42.804 --> 21:44.949
- You let him drive.
- Why wouldn't I?

21:44.973 --> 21:47.007
Because we have no idea
where we are.

21:49.411 --> 21:51.311
Saybird keys about an hour
that way.

21:52.748 --> 21:53.958
If your marine doesn't mess up,

21:53.982 --> 21:55.827
we'll see it
in about 15 minutes.

21:55.851 --> 21:57.729
- Ah.
- We can drop anchor

21:57.753 --> 22:00.053
and party there for the night.
How does that sound?

22:29.751 --> 22:32.897
[VIVIAN] Oh, that was so good.
Thank you. That was delicious.

22:32.921 --> 22:36.768
Woah. My bad, my bad, my bad.
Uh, you need another beer?

22:36.792 --> 22:39.203
Yeah. And could you get me
some paper towels.

22:39.227 --> 22:40.860
Here here's a towel.

22:48.103 --> 22:49.803
[VIVIAN] I'm so full.

22:49.971 --> 22:51.805
- Do you want more?
- Mm-hmm.

22:52.407 --> 22:54.752
There's plenty more below
in my room,

22:54.776 --> 22:57.288
so have as much as you want.

22:57.312 --> 22:58.722
Mmm, thank you.

22:58.746 --> 23:00.158
If we're not hung-over
by tomorrow,

23:00.182 --> 23:01.959
we're doing this wrong,
right Coop?

23:01.983 --> 23:03.063
- [VIVIAN LAUGHING]
- Right.

23:03.919 --> 23:05.719
Oh. Thank you.

23:07.856 --> 23:09.989
[SOFT MUSIC PLAYING]

23:10.125 --> 23:12.365
[JOHN] When was the last time
you guys had a poker night?

23:13.061 --> 23:14.555
What do you say?

23:14.579 --> 23:16.074
- [VIVIAN] I'm game.
- [COOPER] You realize

23:16.098 --> 23:18.259
that everything I know
about poker,

23:18.283 --> 23:20.445
I learned from Danny. So yeah,
I'm down to kick your ass.

23:20.469 --> 23:23.414
Well, if Danny boy taught you,
I am upping the ante,

23:23.438 --> 23:26.951
because he was a terrible
